    <item>
      <title>首席执行官对公司发展充满信心</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-15/rent-the-runway-ceo-confident-in-company-s-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Rent the Runway 的首席执行官兼联合创始人詹妮弗·海曼 (Jennifer Hyman) 表示，她对公司的增长充满信心。 Rent the Runway 公布的第四季度营收和调整后 Ebitda 均高于分析师预期。她在“彭博市场”节目中发表讲话。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-15/rent-the-runway-ceo-confident-in-company-s-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 16:55:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄铝担心新的俄罗斯金属制裁将导致 36% 的销售额面临风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/rusal-fears-new-russia-metal-sanctions-put-36-of-sales-at-risk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯铝业巨头 United Co Rusal International PJSC 担心，由于英国和美国实施的制裁，其多达 36% 的销售额可能面临风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/rusal-fears-new-russia-metal-sanctions-put-36-of-sales-at-risk</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 16:54:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>对于瑞银策略师来说，美联储加息至 6.5% 是“真正的风险”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/fed-hiking-rates-to-6-5-is-real-risk-for-ubs-strategists</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞银集团(UBS Group AG)策略师表示，美国强劲增长和高通胀相结合，加大了美联储加息而不是降息的可能性，从而使明年的借贷成本高达6.5%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/fed-hiking-rates-to-6-5-is-real-risk-for-ubs-strategists</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 16:40:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国开始为最强大的模型起草人工智能法规</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/uk-starts-drafting-ai-regulations-for-most-powerful-models</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士称，英国正在开始起草管理人工智能的法规，重点关注支撑 OpenAI 的 ChatGPT 的最强大的语言模型。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/uk-starts-drafting-ai-regulations-for-most-powerful-models</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 15:49:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加纳财政部长表示债务改革遇到的障碍只是一个小问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/ghana-made-signifcant-progress-in-debt-restructuring-bondholder-talks-continue</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加纳财政部长穆罕默德·阿明·亚当表示，加纳在债务重组谈判中取得了“重大进展”，周一导致其欧元债券暴跌的最新障碍将在与债券持有人的进一步谈判中得到解决。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/ghana-made-signifcant-progress-in-debt-restructuring-bondholder-talks-continue</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 14:13:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国零售销售火爆后，国债收益率跃升至 2024 年新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/treasury-yields-reach-new-2024-highs-after-march-retail-sales</link>
      <description><![CDATA[强劲的零售销售数据进一步削弱了投资者对美联储今年将开始降息的信心，大多数美国国债收益率攀升至今年以来的新高，其中两年期国债收益率接近5%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/treasury-yields-reach-new-2024-highs-after-march-retail-sales</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 12:40:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国数据重新点燃长期走高押注，新兴市场货币下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/emerging-currencies-settle-as-shekel-bounces-back-after-attack</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国零售销售数据远强于预期后，新兴市场货币跌至近三个月来的最低水平，掩盖了中东地缘政治紧张局势缓解带来的风险资产的缓和。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/emerging-currencies-settle-as-shekel-bounces-back-after-attack</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 09:50:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着大型科技股抛售，标准普尔 500 指数跌破 5,100 点：市场结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-14/asian-stocks-set-to-fall-in-wake-of-iran-attack-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在少数大型股下跌的情况下，股市下跌，在零售销售强劲刺激人们押注美联储不会急于降息后，债券收益率攀升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-14/asian-stocks-set-to-fall-in-wake-of-iran-attack-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 22:08:47 GMT</pubDate>
